==Talking to NPCs prior to starting event==
===Talking to Big Dave===
* {{tcond|If the player has not completed [[Fishing Contest]]:}}
** '''Big Dave:''' Hey guy! Always nice to see a fresh face!
** '''Player:''' Hey, who are you?
** '''Big Dave:''' The name's Big Dave! Current champion of the Hemenster fishing contest.
** '''Big Dave:''' I heard there'd be a fishing contest 'round here, so I came to win it.
* {{tcond|If the player has completed Fishing Contest:}}
** '''Big Dave:''' Hey, don't I know you from the Hemenster fishing contest?
** '''Player:''' Big Dave? What are you doing here?
** '''Big Dave:''' Well, I heard there'd be a fishing contest 'round here, so I came to win it.
* '''Big Dave:''' It's strange, though. Doesn't seem like there's even anything in the pond...
* {{tact|end}}

===Capt' Arnav===
* '''Player:''' Hello, Capt' Arnav!
* '''Capt' Arnav:''' Ahoy, [player name], how are you doin'?
* '''Player:''' I'm good thanks! Shouldn't you be out looking for adventurers to help you with your treasure chest?
* '''Capt' Arnav:''' I would normally, but, not t'day!
* '''Player:''' Why not today?
* '''Capt' Arnav:''' I 'ave hidden me treasure chest!
* '''Player:''' I see.
* '''Player:''' Actually, no I don't, why did you do that?
* '''Capt' Arnav:''' It's the 9th birthday o' Gielinor. I be helpin' out with the birthday event!
* '''Capt' Arnav:''' Event goers can go on a treasure hunt to find me chest!
* '''Player:''' Sounds fun! But, 9th birthday? Gielinor is much older than that!
* '''Capt' Arnav:''' Well, aye, but it's the 9th year since we decided to start countin' here!
* '''Player:''' Fair enough I suppose. Can I join the treasure hunt?
* '''Capt' Arnav:''' You can, but ye needs to get permission to join the event first...
* '''Capt' Arnav:''' Talk to Chancellor Hassan in the palace. It's the huge buildin' right next to us.
* {{tact|end}}

===Larry Leprechaun===
* '''Player:''' Hey, what's going on here?
* '''Larry Leprechaun:''' It be a fishin' contest, matey! What does it look like?
* '''Player:''' Can I join in?
* '''Larry Leprechaun:''' Aye, maybe. Go 'n see Chancellor Hassan in the palace. 'Tis the huge building in the south of Al Kharid. Ye can't miss it.
* {{tact|end}}

===My Arm===
* '''Player:''' Hello, My Arm
* '''My Arm:''' Hi human, My Arm running cookout competition. If you want to take part, talk to Hassan in big palace.
* {{tact|end}}

===Cook===
* '''Player:''' Hi cook!
* '''Cook:''' Hello, [player name]. I can't really talk right now sorry, I'm taking part in the cookout!
* '''Cook:''' Speak to My Arm if you'd like to take part.
* {{tact|end}}

===Hans===
* '''Player:''' Hi, Hans!
* '''Hans:''' I can't really talk right now [player name], I'm taking part in the cookout!
* '''Hans:''' Speak to My Arm if you'd like to take part.
* {{tact|end}}

===Wise Old Man===
* '''Player:''' Hello sir!
* '''Wise Old Man:''' Hi, [player name]. I'm a bit busy at the moment, I'm taking part in the cookout!
* '''Wise Old Man:''' Speak to My Arm if you'd like to take part.
* {{tact|end}}

==Starting out==
===Talking to Hassan===
* {{topt|Talk about the birthday event.}}
** '''Hassan:''' Greetings, adventurer. Welcome to Al Kharid. This year, we've been entrusted to host the year's birthday event-
** '''Player:''' -But a swarm of goblins are threatening proceedings?!
** '''Hassan:''' ...No?
** '''Player:''' ...One of the visiting dignitaries has gone missing and needs to be rescued?
** '''Hassan:''' ...No.
** '''Player:''' ...A statue set for display has been decapitated and you need to find the head?
** '''Hassan:''' Adventurer, are you quite alright?
** '''Player:''' Well, usually something goes wrong at these events and you need someone like me to help!
** '''Hassan:''' Ah, I see. Well, you will be disappointed to hear that thus far, everything is going smoothly.
** '''Hassan:''' The Emir knows the benefits of showcasing the city of Al Kharid to a global audience at an event such as this, and has entrusted me to ensure everything runs flawlessly.
** '''Hassan:''' Naturally, I did not fail him.
** '''Player:''' That's all well and good, but why am I even here then?
** '''Hassan:''' Well, if you cannot satisfy yourself in helping the event, perhaps you could satisfy yourself by partaking in it instead?
** {{topt|Yes!}}
*** '''Hassan:''' Wonderful. A few of our visiting dignitaries have set up activities to entertain our guests; I am sure they would greatly appreciate your participation.
*** '''Hassan:''' I'm led to believe you might already know Captain Arnav. He's leading a treasure hunt, and can be found just north-east of the bank.
*** '''Hassan:''' I believe the leprechauns, lead by one named Larry, are hosting a fishing competition over by the oasis, north of the Gem trader.
*** '''Hassan:''' And lastly, we had a request from Trollweiss to allow them to sample some of our cuisine. A troll by the name of My Arm can be found outside the Duel Arena.
*** '''Player:''' And what's in it for me?
*** '''Hassan:''' I'm glad you asked, adventurer. I've been working on a new invention in my spare time, and I am planning to debut it towards the end of the ceremonies.
*** '''Hassan:''' However, if you were to keep our guests engaged by participating in their activities, I would be more than happy to reward you with an advance prototype.
*** '''Hassan:''' Before you leave, take these notes and a quill to keep them updated. I find that's the easiest way to keep track of what needs doing.
*** {{tbox|pic=Notes (2022 Birthday event) detail.png|Hassan hands you a note sheet and a quill.}}
*** '''Hassan:''' The city of Al Kharid wishes you an excellent stay, adventurer.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Hassan:''' Oh. Very well then, let me know if you change your mind.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Talk about something else.}}

===Talking to Hassan again===
* {{topt|Talk about the birthday event.}}
** '''Hassan:''' Greetings, adventurer. How are you enjoying the event?
** {{tcond|If the player lost their [[Notes (2022 Birthday event)|notes]]:}}
*** '''Player:''' Not great, I'm afraid. I've lost my notes!
*** '''Hassan:''' Not to worry. Here's a fresh sheet; I'm sure you can remember what you've done already.
*** {{tbox|pic=Notes (2022 Birthday event) detail.png|Hassan hands you a note sheet and a quill, which you quickly update.}}
*** '''Hassan:''' Do try not to lose this one.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player still has their [[Notes (2022 Birthday event)|notes]]:}}
*** '''Player:''' It's great, but I still need to do some activities.
*** '''Hassan:''' Very well. Do enjoy yourself, adventurer.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Talk about something else.}}

==Larry's Fishing Contest==
===Talking to Larry Leprechaun===
* '''Player:''' Hello, is this where the fishing contest is taking place?
* '''Larry Leprechaun:''' Aye, it is. Roight in that oasis o'er there.
* '''Player:''' So what are the rules?
* '''Larry Leprechaun:''' Nothin' fancy. Whoever pulls the biggest fish out of that pond is the winner.
* '''Larry Leprechaun:''' Weirdly, nobody's managed to catch any fish yet...
* '''Larry Leprechaun:''' Ah well. I'm sure somebody'll catch something in time.
* '''Player:''' Can I join in then?
* '''Larry Leprechaun:''' Ah, yer more than welcome te try. Though, ye'll be needin' some fishing supplies. I can give you some, if ye'd like.
* {{topt|Yes please!}}
** '''Player:''' Yes please!
** {{tbox|pic=Fishing rod detail.png|pic2=Fishing bait detail.png|Larry hands you a fishing rod and some bait.}}
** '''Larry Leprechaun:''' There ye go. Come back t' me if ye need anythin' else.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|No thanks, I'll get my own.}}
** '''Player:''' No thanks, I'll get my own.
** '''Larry Leprechaun:''' Suit yerself. Ye'll probably want a normal fishing rod and some bait.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Larry again===
* '''Larry Leprechaun:''' Ah, hello there! Any luck wit' the fish?
* '''Player:''' No, not yet.
* '''Larry Leprechaun:''' Ah well. Is there anything I can do for you in the meanwhile?
* {{tcond|If player has no fishing supplies:}}
** '''Player:''' Could I have some fishing supplies?
** {{tbox|pic=Fishing rod detail.png|pic2=Fishing bait detail.png|Larry hands you a fishing rod and some bait.}}
** '''Larry Leprechaun:''' See me again if ye need anythin' else.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If player has fishing supplies:}}
** '''Player:''' Not right now, thanks.
** '''Larry Leprechaun:''' Suit yourself. I'll be relaxing here if you need anything.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Big Dave===
* {{tcond|If the player has not completed [[Fishing Contest]]:}}
** '''Big Dave:''' Hey guy! Always nice to see a fresh face!
** '''Player:''' Hey, who are you?
** '''Big Dave:''' The name's Big Dave! Current champion of the Hemenster fishing contest.
** '''Big Dave:''' I heard there'd be a fishing contest 'round here, so I came to win it.
* {{tcond|If the player has completed Fishing Contest:}}
** '''Big Dave:''' Hey, don't I know you from the Hemenster fishing contest?
** '''Player:''' Big Dave? What are you doing here?
** '''Big Dave:''' Well, I heard there'd be a fishing contest 'round here, so I came to win it.
* '''Big Dave:''' It's strange, though. Doesn't seem like there's even anything in the pond...
* '''Player:''' So have you caught anything?
* '''Big Dave:''' Nah, there are clearly fish there, but nothing I brought as bait seems to be able to coax them out...
* '''Big Dave:''' I reckon I need some local bait, but there's not a fishing shop nearby.
* '''Big Dave:''' Only person I can think that would sell some is that merchant over east by the cook out, but he seems like the kinda guy who would try to sell you a raw chicken if you just talked to him.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Ali Morrisane===
* {{topt|Talk about the birthday event.}}
** '''Ali Morrisane:''' Greetings, friend. Can I help you?
** '''Player:''' This is going to sound crazy, but do you have any fishing bait that I could use to fish in a desert oasis?
** '''Ali Morrisane:''' Ah, you're taking part in the leprechaun's fishing contest then, are you? Yes, I have something that should help with that.
** '''Player:''' Great! How much do you want for it?
** '''Ali Morrisane:''' Well... this is an unusual request, but could I ask a favour? I need something collected, but with all the tourists in Al Kharid, I need to maintain my position at my stall.
** '''Player:''' Sure, I guess. What do you need?
** '''Ali Morrisane:''' You know the saying, knowledge is power? I commissioned a report from the Emir's spymaster Osman on trade activities from Brimhaven. Can I trust you to collect it?
** '''Player:''' Certainly. Where is Osman?
** '''Ali Morrisane:''' He should be outside the palace. Go switfly, my friend.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Talk about something else.}}

===Talking to Osman===
* {{topt|Talk about the birthday event.}}
** '''Player:''' Hello, Ali Morrisane sent me to collect a trade report.
** '''Osman:''' He did, did he? Well, that's mighty convenient, isn't it?
** '''Osman:''' Well, naturally, if he sent you, you'll have no problems answering the security question then?
** '''Player:''' Oh... ehrm... sure...?
** '''Osman:''' How many crates are around Ali Morrisane's stall?
** {{tcond|If the player inputs the wrong answer:}}
*** '''Osman:''' No, that's not it. Go get the answer, I'll wait here.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player inputs the correct answer:}}
*** '''Osman:''' Yes, that's the answer. Here's the report.
*** {{tbox|pic=Osman's report detail.png|Osman hands you the report.}}
*** '''Player:''' That didn't sound like a particularly secure security question!
*** '''Osman:''' Ali Morrisane agreed to it and I've already got his pay. If he's fine with random adventurers potentially stealing the report, so be it.
*** '''Osman:''' Not that an adventurer like you would be able to decipher the code it's written in anyway.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Talk about something else.}}

====Talking to Osman before answering the question====
* {{topt|Talk about the birthday event.}}
** '''Osman:''' Have you the answer to the security question?
** '''Player:''' Uh... yes?
** '''Osman:''' How many crates are around Ali Morrisane's stall?
** {{tcond|If the player inputs the wrong answer:}}
*** '''Osman:''' No, that's not it. Go get the answer, I'll wait here.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player inputs the correct answer:}}
*** '''Osman:''' Yes, that's the answer. Here's the report.
*** {{tbox|pic=Osman's report detail.png|Osman hands you the report.}}
*** '''Player:''' That didn't sound like a particularly secure security question!
*** '''Osman:''' Ali Morrisane agreed to it and I've already got his pay. If he's fine with random adventurers potentially stealing the report, so be it.
*** '''Osman:''' Not that an adventurer like you would be able to decipher the code it's written in anyway.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Talk about something else.}}

====Talking to Osman again====
* {{topt|Talk about the birthday event.}}
* {{tcond|If the player lost Osman's report:}}
** '''Player:''' No, I think I lost it.
** '''Osman:''' Well, it's a good thing the message was encoded. I can give you another copy. Do try to keep this one secure.
** {{tbox|pic=Osman's report detail.png|Osman hands you another copy of the report.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has not yet delivered Osman's report:}}
** '''Osman:''' Have you delivered the report yet?
** '''Player:''' Not yet, no.
** '''Osman:''' Well, I would hurry. Trade information tends to be rather time-sensitive.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player delivered Osman's report:}}
** '''Player:''' Hey Osman, I-
** '''Osman:''' I don't believe we have any reason to talk right now. In case you hadn't noticed, there's quite a few visiting dignitaries that I need to keep an eye on.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Talk about something else.}}

===Delivering the report to Ali Morrisane===
* {{topt|Talk about the birthday event.}}
** '''Ali Morrisane:''' Greetings, friend. Have you gathered the intel?
** {{tcond|If the player has not yet obtained Osman's report:}}
*** '''Player:''' Not yet, sorry.
*** '''Ali Morrisane:''' Well, I would suggest going to collect it. That information could be very time-sensitive!
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player has obtained Osman's report:}}
*** '''Player:''' Yes, I have it right here!
*** '''Ali Morrisane:''' Let's see what we've got here... hm....
*** '''Ali Morrisane:''' ...Chocolate? In the desert? Hm... not a terrible idea, but how to stop it from melting...?
*** '''Ali Morrisane:''' Well, adventurer, this report has given me quite a bit to consider. I can certainly say you've more than earned this bait.
*** {{tbox|pic=Desert bait detail.png|Ali Morrisane hands you some weird looking fishing bait.}}
*** '''Ali Morrisane:''' Use this with a fishing rod at that oasis and you are guaranteed a catch.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Talk about something else.}}

===Talking to Ali Morrisane again===
* {{topt|Talk about the birthday event.}}
** '''Ali Morrisane:''' How goes the fishing?
** {{tcond|If the player lost the desert bait:}}
*** '''Player:''' Not great, I'm afraid. I've lost the bait!
*** {{tcond|If the player has inventory space:}}
**** '''Ali Morrisane:''' How unfortunate. Well, with these festivities, I do feel rather generous. Have some more bait.
**** {{tact|Ali Morrisane gives the player desert bait.}}
**** {{tact|end}}
*** {{tcond|If the player does not have inventory space:}}
**** '''Ali Morrisane:''' How unfortunate. Well, with these festivities, I do feel rather generous. Clear some space in your inventory, and I will give you some more bait.
**** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player has not used the desert bait:}}
*** '''Player:''' It's... ok? I haven't tried using your bait yet, though.
*** '''Ali Morrisane:''' I would recommend trying it. In all my years in Al Kharid, this bait is the only thing I know of capable of drawing fish from these waters.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player has used the desert bait:}}
*** '''Player:''' Well, I managed to catch this tiny fish, but I'm not sure it'll win me the contest.
*** '''Ali Morrisane:''' Well, I can assure you nobody else has come to me for advice yet. That fish will almost certainly be all you need to attain victory.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|event=No|Talk about something else.}}

