====Using normal bait====
* {{mes|You cast out your line...}}
* {{mes|You attempt to catch a fish.}}
* {{mes|Still trying...}}
* {{mes|Still trying...}}
* {{mes|Any day now...}}
* {{mes|This doesn't seem to be working...}}
